er this weekafter the American Jewish Community called them out.\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Jews\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"American Jewish Community\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Jews\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Adidas\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"the connections\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"line\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"theapology\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 484}, {\"ngram\": \"earlier this weekafter\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time they specifically apologized to their partners too ... saying sorry in their statement to Hadid,A$AP Nast,Jules Kound\\u00e9and others for the impact this may have had on them and their careers.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their partners\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"their statement\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 664}, {\"ngram\": \"Hadid\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"A$AP Nast\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"their careers\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Apologizing to their models marks a huge step for Adidas ... and, one that can be seen as doing some damage control -- 'cause we know at least one of them's considering legal remedies.\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 0.9999999999891998, \"rank\": 1.0796020350310085e-11, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their models\", \"fr